fields.description: From clicking stunning landscape photos to fast multitasking, the Panasonic P100 is a smartphone for the impulsive and flamboyant millennials. Powered by a 1.25 GHz quad-core processor with 1 GB of RAM, this smartphone runs on the Android Nougat 7.0 for an efficient, smooth multitasking.
